queries.all:
SELECT * FROM
(personal_data OUTER JOIN sis_academic_career 
ON personal_data.student_token = sis_academic_career.student_token) AS career
OUTER JOIN
((sis_academic_program_offer OUTER JOIN sis_academic_program
ON sis_academic_program_offer.academic_program = sis_academic_program.academic_program) AS program1)
OUTER JOIN sis_academic_program_offer
 ON program1.dual_academic_program = sis_academic_program_offer.academic_program) AS program
ON career.student_token = program.student_token
OUTER JOIN
(sis_plan_offer OUTER JOIN sis_academic_plan
ON sis_plan_offer.academic_plan = sis_academic_plan.academic_plan) AS plan
ON career.student_token = plan.student_token AND 
career.academic_career = plan.academic_career AND
   program.academic_program = plan.academic_program
OUTER JOIN sis_enrolment
ON sis_enrolment.student_token = plan.student_token AND 
sis_enrolment.academic_program = plan.academic_program AND
sis_enrolment.academic_plan = plan.academic_plan
